msgid ""
"If you have questions or comments about these guidelines themselves, feel "
"free to send those to &lt;<a class=\"reference\" href=\"mailto:licensing@fsf."
"org\">licensing@fsf.org</a>&gt;.  We hope that they help everyone better "
"understand the issues that are important for free system distributions, and "
"we look forward to promoting more of them in the future."
msgstr ""
"إذا كانت لديك أي أسئلة أو تعليقات عن هذه التوجيهات والإرشادات، فلا تتردد في "
